Package: DIVASpackage
Type: Package
Title: Data Integration via Analysis of Subspaces
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Yinuo", "Sun", , "yinuo.sun.1@unimelb.edu.au", role = "aut"),
  person("Jiadong", "Mao", , "chiatungmao@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3818-1981")))
Maintainer: Jiadong Mao <chiatungmao@gmail.com>
Description: Based on 'Data integration via analysis of subspaces (DIVAS)',
    this is a package that implements the DIVAS methodology for data integration using subspace analysis.
    This package provides tools for signal extraction, noise estimation, and joint structure identification
    from high-dimensional datasets, useful in multi-omics and other complex data scenarios. 
